; The `D` detune MML command adds a fixed VxPITCH offset to all
; subsequent play-note and portamento instructions.
; `D0` disables detune.

A D0   c r16
A D+80 c r16
A D-80 c r16
A r

A D0    {eg} r16
A D+100 {eg} r16
A D-100 {eg} r16
